Signed-off-by: Daniel Vetter <daniel.vetter@ffwll.ch>

--

Testing feedback highgly welcome, and thanks for Benoit for finding
out that the bpc computations are busted.
-Daniel

Acked-by: Michal Srb <msrb@suse.com>
